            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Start with a clean face. I like to use a gentle cleanser to remove any makeup or impurities—this ensures the light penetrates effectively. Pat dry and avoid heavy serums beforehand; the mask works best on bare skin.",
