            "text": "Position the Mask",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Place the mask over your face, adjusting the straps for a snug, comfortable fit. The ergonomic design means it contours well without pressure points, so you can relax completely.",
