            "_type": "span",
            "text": ": Power on the device and choose your preferred setting. For beginners, start with the standard 10-minute session. The mask has an auto-timer, so you can just sit back—maybe read a book or listen to a podcast. I often use this time for mindfulness, turning my skincare into a self-care ritual.",
